The paperwork has been signed and the deal has finally been inked in by our record label. On behalf of Destiny Records, Chesney Claire and I—along with The Robert Abernathy Band, will performing at the AT&T Concert Series in Miami, Florida with Snoop Dogg, Gloria Estefan, Pit Bull, Shakirra and The Miami Symphony Orchestra & Emilio Estefan. 

This event will be streamed globally in April. Right now we are looking at April 6th. 

There is also a Corporate Sponsor Package attached to the flyer if your Corporation/business is interested in getting in on the perks that will come with this event. If you have questions about becoming a sponsor, see the email below on the graphic. 

Meanwhile I’ll be keeping Country Alive on that stage and representing all of you for supporting me all these years. Love you guys. #keepingcountryalive #music #upcomingartist #pop #countrymusic #hiphop @snoopdogg @pitbull @gloriaestefan
